HEADWORD: Advoke
<hw>Ad*voke"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>advocare</ets>. See <er>Advocate</er>.]</ety> <def>To summon; to
call.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Queen Katharine had privately prevailed with the pope to
<qex>advoke</qex> the cause to Rome.</q> <rj><qau>Fuller.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

